WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
After twenty seven years in prison, Nelson Mandela walked free into a waiting world.

00:06.000 --> 00:12.000
His release became a symbol of hope, change, and a new chapter for South Africa.

00:12.000 --> 00:20.000
This story traces the struggle, the patience, and the history behind that unforgettable moment.
